      "seed": 1988521035,
      "version": 39,
      "versionNonce": 1279569259,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783425360218,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Local websocket package may\nnot be packaged.\nmain.py imports \n\"from websocket.manager\nimport manager\"\nBut pyproject.toml only includes\napp and excalidraw as packages\nThat means if installed via the\npackage build, the local\nwebsocket module may not be\nincluded",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "j0NFTG1IS_q4tZQXLeHcl",
      "originalText": "Local websocket package may not be packaged.\nmain.py imports \n\"from websocket.manager import manager\"\nBut pyproject.toml only includes app and excalidraw as packages\nThat means if installed via the package build, the local websocket module may not be included",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    }
  ],
